title.Name: title
title.Value: Northshore Hills Road Race - Group 4 - Race 5

description.Name: description
description.Value:
Event:  2013 NSH Road Race (G4)
Round:  2
Cars:  BMW M1 vs. Olds 442
Teams:  Flying Circus vs. Grand Junk

The BMW M1 from team Flying Circus got its second victory of the week today when it faced off with the old HW Redline model on the road course.  The Olds 442 looked pretty good in the 1st round, but the M1 was a little tougher competition than the 300C was.  Team Grand Junk is eliminated with this result while team Flying Circus and the BMW will be moving onto the Group 4 final.  Come back tomorrow to find out who the other finalist will be between the 24/7 and the Lotus Elise.
